import Input from "./components/Input";
import Button from "./components/Button";

import { Container , Content, Row} from "./styles";
import {useState} from 'react';


function App() {
  const [currentNumber, setCurrentNumber] = useState(0);
  
  return (
    <Container>
      <Content>
        <Input/>
        <Row>
          <Button label="x"/>
          <Button label="/"/>
          <Button label="C"/>
          <Button label="0"/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label="7"/>
          <Button label="8"/>
          <Button label="9"/>
          <Button label="-"/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label="4"/>
          <Button label="5"/>
          <Button label="6"/>
          <Button label="+"/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label="1"/>
          <Button label="2"/>
          <Button label="3"/>
          <Button label="="/>
        </Row>
      </Content>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
